<FIRST>r w AM-Thatcher     11-15 0511</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Thatcher,500</SECOND>
<HEAD>Thatcher To Meet With Reagan, Bush, Greenspan and Sakharov During
Visit</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Will be topped after 7:15 p.m. arrival</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By RUTH SINAI</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
