epresents their will.'' He said the kingdom will `` continue to support the <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> in its efforts to insure the national rights of the <LOCATION> Palestinian </LOCATION> people, including their right to self-determination and the creation of their independent state on their national soil.''
